hrome P-450 enzyme (P450scc) that yields the steroid precursor, pregnenolone (Besman et al. 1989). The cholesterol transfer within the mitochondria is the rate-limiting step in the production of steroid hormones. Therefore reduced amount/activity of the StAR impairs the cholesterol delivery that is necessary for the hormone biosynthesis.", "timestamp": "Mon Jun 08 14:31:46 +0000 2026"}